Package: snippetsaddin
Type: Package
Title: RStudio add-in to add some code snippets, or help with code editing
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person( "Juraj", "Sofranko", role = c("aut", "cre")
                 , email="replace_with_my_first_name.replace_with_my_last_name@gmail.com")
Description: RStudio add-in to add some code snippets, or help with code
    editing. In the current release it contains pipe insertion and its
    surroundings reformatting and slashes reversing.
